dent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">乌木，斯瓦希里语叫它</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">mpingo</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">，英文中叫</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">ebony,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">它是世界名贵的稀有木种之一，主要产于亚洲热带和非洲，其原木的</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">树皮为深灰色，芯材分为黑色</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">深褐色</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">紫红色和带条纹浅褐色等四种。木质优良，耐磨</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">不蛀</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">不腐，比重大于水，极其坚硬，一经打磨十分光滑。非洲人视乌木</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">为神圣，鲜活有生命的。当艺人们雕刻乌木时他们便与乌木开始了交流和沟通，乌木多变的纹理和它自然生成的奇特怪状，会给艺人带来遐想，引导他们去奇思妙想。</span></p><p class=\"MsoFooter\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><br><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoFooter\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">乌木的生长期之长可算木材之最，二</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">三百年才能长成</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">厘米左右树径。在浩瀚的非洲原始森林，唯有乌木是三三两两地独居于万木之中，它们不成</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">林，也不成萌。树木干枯，树叶稀少且小，并微黄带绿。它们虽无其他树种的茂密高大，朝气勃勃，但却显得老成坚韧。近年来，由于砍伐速度加快，乌木越来越少</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">了，直径</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">30CM</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">以上的更是罕见，有些出产乌木的国家</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">已禁止乌木原木出口。</span></p><p class=\"MsoFooter\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><br><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoFooter\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">世纪初开始，非洲乌木雕，已成为欧美等发达国家居室内环境的一种装饰和时尚，它青铜般的尊贵气质，玉石般的珠宝光泽，增添了室内空间的个性化艺术氛围。据非洲当地人认为，乌黑的木头可以为人们辟邪，带来好运。</span></p><p class=\"MsoFooter\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><br><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoFooter\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">近几年，越来越多的中国人开始喜欢上了简约拙朴造型，具有灵动之气和神秘韵味的非洲木雕。为此，我们把来自原产地非洲大陆，造型各异的木雕精品呈现给大家，它无论是用来欣赏</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">收藏</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">还是装饰居室，都是一种极具个性的选择，作为馈赠亲友的珍奇礼品，更是分量十足。</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,'2011-06-12 22:45:25','',0,309,0,2,'乌木，斯瓦希里语叫它mpingo，英文中叫ebony,它是世界名贵的稀有木种之一，主要产于亚洲热带和非洲，其原木的&nbsp;树皮为深灰色，芯材分为黑色.深褐色.紫红色和带条纹浅褐色等四种。木质优良，耐磨.不蛀.不腐，比重大于水，极其坚硬，一经打磨十分光滑。非洲人视乌木&nbsp;为神圣，鲜活有生命的。当艺人们雕刻乌木时他们便与乌木开始了交流和沟通，乌木多变的纹理和它自然生成的奇特怪状，会给艺人带来遐想，引导他们去奇思妙想。','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,0,1),(7,1,'红木小知识','','','<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>ZH-CN</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\r\n  