ly:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、最炎热的大陆<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">非洲是<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>阿非利加洲<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>的简称<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>希腊文<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>阿非利加<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>是阳光灼热的意思。非洲大陆地跨南北半球<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>赤道横贯非洲的中部<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>有<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 3/4 </span>的土地受到太阳的垂直照射<span lang=\"EN-US\"> ,</span>年平均气温在摄氏<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 20 </span>度以上的热带占全洲的<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 95% , </span>其中有一半以上地区终年炎热<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>有<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>热带大陆<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>的称号<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>成为世界上最炎热的大陆。\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、国家分布最多的大洲<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">目前全世界有<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 232</span>个国家和地区。其中非洲有<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 57 </span>个<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>排在各大洲之首<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>在这<span lang=\"EN-US\">57</span>个国家和地区中<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>有<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 53</span>个独立国。另外<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 5 </span>个地区<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>虽然在地理位置上划归非洲<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>但并非均是非洲人的天下<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>大多为法、英两国的领地。如留尼汪为法国的<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>海外省<span lang=\"EN-US\">”, </span>圣赫勒拿为英国<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>直属殖民地<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>。\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、黑人分布最多的大洲<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">非洲是黑人的故乡。黑色人种约占非洲总人口的<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 2/3( </span>约<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 5 </span>亿<span lang=\"EN-US\">) ,</span>主要居住在\r\n撒哈拉沙漠以南<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>是世界黑色人种最多的大洲。 <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、热带草原气候分布最广的大洲 <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">由于非洲特殊的纬度位置<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>使得非洲大陆在全球的气压带和风带中处于对称的位置<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>再加上整个大陆地形相对比较平坦<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>导致受赤道低气压带和信风带影响的面积比其他洲大<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>同时由于赤道附近地区受地势<span lang=\"EN-US\">( </span>东非高原<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>的影响<span lang=\"EN-US\"> ,</span>也形成了热带草原气<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>这样使其成为世界上热带草原气候分布面积最广<span lang=\"EN-US\">( </span>最大<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>的一洲。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、热带雨林气候分布纬度最高的大洲<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">非洲的马达加斯加岛东部因受地形、东南信风和暖流的影响<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>形成了高温多雨的热带雨林气候<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>其分布的纬度超过了南回归线<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>是世界上热带雨林气候分布纬度最高的地区。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、沙漠面积最大的大洲<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">受地理纬度、轮廓和地形等因素的影响<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>非洲大陆受副热带高气压带和信风带控制面积大<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>干旱地区广。非洲的沙漠面积约占全洲面积<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 1/3 , </span>为沙漠面积最大的一洲。撒哈拉沙漠是世界上最大的沙漠<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>面积<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 954 </span>万平方千米<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>西南部还有纳米布沙漠和卡拉哈迪沙漠。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、人口增长最快的大洲<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">非洲目前人口已接近<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 8 </span>亿。人口的自然增长率达到了<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 28‰, </span>是目前世界上人口自然增长率最高的大洲<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>也是人口增长最快的大洲。主要原因是二次大战后<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>非洲民族解放运动蓬勃发展<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>民族经济有所发展。由于医疗卫生事业的不断进步<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>死亡率不断降低<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>加上高出生率的影响<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>使人口的自然增长率一直处于较高的状态。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\" lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">、经济最不发达的大洲 <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">据联合国宣布<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>世界上最不发达的<span lang=\"EN-US\">48 </span>个国家中有<span lang=\"EN-US\">\r\n33 </span>个是非洲国家<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>最不发达国家占非洲国家总数的<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 62% </span>。非洲成为世界上经济最不发达的地区有着很深的历史根源<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>如长期被西方殖民国家掠夺<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>生产力的极其落后<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>其次是战争和动乱不停。在非洲的一些国家动辄就是发生政变、种族分裂<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>结果是生民涂炭<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>几十万人遭受大屠杀<span lang=\"EN-US\"> , </span>更不要谈发展经济了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,'2011-06-14 13:10:19','',0,265,0,2,'非洲的世界之最(二)','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,0,1),(12,3,'非洲音乐的灵魂——鼓','','','<!--[if gte mso 9]><x